name: VR Jungle Passthrough Handtracking
summary:
Create a detailed jungle in your home using passthrough
o 70+ Plants & jungle objects
o 60+ Animals
o 5+ bonus pieces of furniture

Plants, animals, and furniture can be moved, deleted, or respawned (random spawners for each)

Various levels include:
- Randomly spawned jungles
- Ability to spawn and add plants, animals, and furniture to edit each level
- Premade room sizes (10x10 and 30x30 feet)

Animals: elephants, tigers, leopards, lions, croc, turtle, dinos, birds, farm animals, and many more
